---
title: Creole Salmon & Roast Veggie Toss with Caramelised Onion Chutney & Mayo
description: This heavenly salmon coated in our Creole spice blend is full of flavour, thanks to red bell pepper, onion and garlic.
Add a medley of veggies and a dollop of our garlic aioli and it’s satisfaction, guaranteed!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
